{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection","text":"CLLocationDirection","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The value ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"text":" means that the top edge of the map view corresponds to true","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"north. The value ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"90"},{"text":" means the top of the map is pointing due east. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"180"},{"text":" means the top of the map points due south, and so on.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setDirection:animated:"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The heading of the map, measured in degrees clockwise from true north."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"direction","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)direction","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1081"}},"hierarchy":